General Notes:
*Torpedo Cruisers are light cruisers remodelled to arm a massive quantity of torpedoes. In this game, they are the only few cruisers that are able to equip midget submarines for a preemptive torpedo strike, [[Type A Ko-hyoteki]].
*Torpedo cruisers have the highest torpedo stat among light cruisers, making them terrifically deadly night combatants.
*Light cruiser [[Kiso]] remodels into a torpedo cruiser with her second remodel at level 65.
*Kitakami and Ooi have very low first remodel level, level 10. They can be used as an easy source of [[61cm Quad (Oxygen) Torpedo Mount]].
*All torpedo cruisers at their second remodel have a valuable [[61cm Quint (Oxygen) Torpedo Mount]] as default equipment.



